notesStmt.note: This conversation is between two people and takes place on a Saturday morning. S1 and S2 are a couple, hence the conversation is very informal. They talk about and discuss what they could cook that day. They briefly speak about a cooking program which they have watched on TV. While S2 is looking for recipes on the internet, S1 tells S2 about an Austrian restaurant which she went to the day before. S1 speaks about what she had to eat and drink there, which results in a brief discussion about different kinds of coffee. S1 also tells S2 about an encounter with a mouse in her office the day before. The speakers come to an agreement as to what they will cook. They decide that they will go to an Argentinian coffee house on the way and get ready to leave.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
